OL,3,CHow and where to see Perseid meteor
OL,4,Cshower across UK skies
OL,6,FShooting stars will be visible across
OL,7,Fthe UK during the annual Perseid
OL,8,Fmeteor shower that will reach its peak
OL,9,Fon Tuesday night.
OL,11,FWhile about 150 meteors will cross the
OL,12,Fsky per hour, only up to 100 of them
OL,13,Fmight be visible.
OL,15,FThe meteor shower occurs every summer.
OL,16,FThis year's has already been running
OL,17,Ffor several weeks but is expected to
OL,18,Fbe most visible on Tuesday night.
OL,20,FWhere can I see it?
