OL,3,CHow and where to see Perseid meteor
OL,4,Cshower across UK skies
OL,6,FThe meteor shower will be visible
OL,7,Facross all of the UK, but will be most
OL,8,Fvisible in the north-east of the UK as
OL,9,Fthe sun sets.
OL,11,FThe further south you go, the lower
OL,12,FPerseid sits on the horizon, making
OL,13,Fthe spectacle harder to see.
OL,15,FExperts say stargazers have a better
OL,16,Fchance of seeing shooting stars in
OL,17,Fareas with less light pollution.
