OL,3,CHow and where to see Perseid meteor
OL,4,Cshower across UK skies
OL,6,FRoyal Observatory Greenwich astronomer
OL,7,FEd Bloomer said: "Getting into the
OL,8,Fmiddle of a field in the south east of
OL,9,FEngland, in London, is going to be
OL,10,Fbetter than being in the middle of
OL,11,FAberdeen," Dr Bloomer said.
OL,13,FWhen and how can I see it?
OL,15,FOnce the sun sets, clear skies will
OL,16,Fafford good visibility on Tuesday
OL,17,Fnight, although a waning full moon
OL,18,Fmight make it brighter than normal and
OL,19,Fobscure the perfect view.
