OL,3,CHow and where to see Perseid meteor
OL,4,Cshower across UK skies
OL,6,FThe meteor shower will be best seen
OL,7,Fpre-dawn, but can also be visible from
OL,8,Flate at night.
OL,10,FFind a place well away from street
OL,11,Flamps, Dr Bloomer advises. Switch off
OL,12,Fany house lights if you are looking
OL,13,Fout from your garden.
OL,15,FDr Bloomer said you will need to allow
OL,16,Ftime to let your eyes adjust to the
OL,17,Fdark before the meteor shower could be
OL,18,Fseen.
