OL,3,CHow and where to see Perseid meteor
OL,4,Cshower across UK skies
OL,6,FHe recommended viewers take a camping
OL,7,Fchair or a rug, sit down outside away
OL,8,Ffrom any light source and wait about
OL,9,Fhalf an hour.
OL,11,FShooting stars generally only last a
OL,12,Fsecond or two and sometimes appear in
OL,13,Fflurries.
OL,15,FIf you're struggling to see the meteor
OL,16,Fshower, Dr Bloomer suggested turning
OL,17,Fyour head and watching through
OL,18,Fperipheral vision (side vision) as it
OL,19,Fcan be easier to see in low light
OL,20,Fconditions.
