OL,11,FWhat is a Perseid meteor shower?
OL,13,FEvery summer the Earth hits a trail of
OL,14,Fdebris from the Swift-Tuttle comet as
OL,15,Fit orbits the sun.
OL,17,FSpecks as small as a grain of dust
OL,18,Fflare up under the pressure of the
OL,19,Fplanet's atmosphere and create
OL,20,Fshooting stars and a long trail of
OL,21,Flight and colour.
