OL,3,CHow and where to see Perseid meteor
OL,4,Cshower across UK skies
OL,6,FPerseid is considered the best meteor
OL,7,Fshower of the year and peaks in mid
OL,8,FAugust.
OL,10,FPerseids are also known for their
OL,11,Ffireballs, which are larger explosions
OL,12,Fof light and colour and bigger than
OL,13,Fthe average meteor streak.
OL,15,FThis meteor shower has already been
OL,16,Frunning for a few weeks and will
OL,17,Fcontinue until around August 24.
